    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv its slower, but its much cheaper. Algolia charges per search request, 100ms delay is a very reasonable compromise for businesses that have a budget. \r\n\r\nAlso, i'm not delaying every request, `clearTimeout` negates previous requests if the next character is typed",
